thread.title: Greg Gentry

author: Greg Gentry
title: Greg Gentry
text:
Just received a CD EP and poster project back from Wholesale Tape and Supply. Very smooth process and their online communication system works very well.
CD's were of very high quality as was the print materials. All of this for a great price.
I also like how you can order a minimum of 100 CD's (I ordered 200) and you can reorder more with no extra setup charge. This will allow me to order as I go and not have to keep a lot of CD's in inventory.
